  "componentDescriptions": {
    "DescriptionItem": "Par key-value. Layout: stacked (term arriba) / horizontal (side-by-side) / inline (term: description en línea). Size: sm/md/lg. Emphasis: term / description / equal (cuál recibe más peso visual).\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <dt>+<dd> native\n• Term icon aria-hidden='true'\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• No focusable\n\nWCAG 2.2 AA.",
    "DescriptionList": "Display de pares term/description (metadata, details panels, order summaries). Columns: 1 (stacked list) / 2 (two-column grid) / 3 (three-column). Dividers: none/between/all.\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <dl> native\n• DOM order lineal (term → description alternando)\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• No focusable\n\nTokens: 14, prefijo dl-.\nWCAG 2.2 AA.\n\nScope: metadata displays (User profile fields, order summary, product attributes, settings preview). Para editable key-value usa Form.\n\nNative HTML <dl><dt><dd> es el único element HTML diseñado para este pattern — accessibility built-in."
  },
